308
00:35:59,115 --> 00:36:01,413
That fever, man,

309
00:36:01,576 --> 00:36:05,126
her skin gave off
a heat like a furnace.

310
00:36:10,460 --> 00:36:11,837
I should've--

311
00:36:12,003 --> 00:36:14,347
I should've put her down, man.
I should've put her down.

312
00:36:14,506 --> 00:36:16,053
I know that, but I--

313
