you know what?
I just didn't have it in me.

314
00:36:25,725 --> 00:36:27,819
She's the mother of my child.

315
00:36:53,837 --> 00:36:55,714
Are we sure they're dead?

316
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:58,759
