Our photo albums,
family pictures" all gone.

334
00:38:14,501 --> 00:38:18,426
Photo albums.

335
00:38:22,133 --> 00:38:25,683
My wife-- same thing.

336
00:38:25,845 --> 00:38:27,893
There I am
packing survival gear,

337
00:38:28,056 --> 00:38:30,479
she's grabbing photo alb...

