00:47:30,014 --> 00:47:31,607
Jenny.

418
00:47:32,975 --> 00:47:34,693
Come on, baby.

419
00:48:05,383 --> 00:48:07,556
I'm sorry this happened to you.

420
00:49:02,440 --> 00:49:04,192
Come on. Come on.

